---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About wc notes"
	description="About this personal blog and public notebook."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-04-30')}
>
	<p>
		wc notes is a small public notebook for writing down useful ideas, technical notes, AI observations, tools, and resources.
	</p>
	<p>
		The site is intentionally simple: Markdown-first, static, fast, version-controlled, and easy to move elsewhere.
	</p>
	<h2>Stack</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Astro for the static site.</li>
		<li>GitHub for source control.</li>
		<li>Cloudflare Pages or another free static host for deployment.</li>
		<li>Pagefind for local static search.</li>
		<li>Utterances for GitHub-based comments.</li>
	</ul>
</Layout>
